id="usage-guildlines"><div class=""><div class="p-2 text-sm marker:dark:text-white"><hr class="mt-0">  <p>Before diving into these NCERT Solutions for Maths, Physics, Chemistry, and Biology, here are some essential tips and tricks to optimize your experience with our video tutorials:</p> <h3> Distraction-Free Study Environment </h3> <p>Subjects like Mathematics, Physics, Chemistry, and Biology demand undivided attention. To make the most of these NCERT video tutorials, ensure you're in a distraction-free study environment. Opt for a serene and noise-free room, which will aid in comprehending and solving intricate problems across all subjects. Moreover, forming a study group with friends can be beneficial. It provides an avenue to discuss and resolve challenging questions together.</p> <h3>Prepare Your Notes</h3> <p>Taking notes while watching the videos is one of the simplest yet most effective strategies. Always have a journal handy to jot down crucial points and formulas. This practice not only aids in information retention but also provides a quick reference for future revisions. Plus, you can always revisit the videos for expert insights!</p> <h3>Face the Doubts</h3> <p>Subjects like Maths are all about practice. If you find yourself stuck on a particular problem, break it down step by step in a notebook. Patience and persistence are key to mastering these subjects. Over time, this practice will significantly enhance your problem-solving abilities.</p> <h3>NCERT Solutions Preparation Tips for All</h3> <p>Subjects like Mathematics are methodical and, at times, philosophical. They involve numerous formulas and steps to arrive at a definitive solution. some essential tips and tricks to optimize your experience with our video tutorials:</p> <h3> Distraction-Free Study Environment </h3> <p>Subjects like Mathematics, Physics, Chemistry, and Biology demand undivided attention. To make the most of these NCERT video tutorials, ensure you're in a distraction-free study environment. Opt for a serene and noise-free room, which will aid in comprehending and solving intricate problems across all subjects. Moreover, forming a study group with friends can be beneficial. It provides an avenue to discuss and resolve challenging questions together.</p> <h3>Prepare Your Notes</h3> <p>Taking notes while watching the videos is one of the simplest yet most effective strategies. Always have a journal handy to jot down crucial points and formulas. This practice not only aids in information retention but also provides a quick reference for future revisions. Plus, you can always revisit the videos for expert insights!</p> <h3>Face the Doubts</h3> <p>Subjects like Maths are all about practice. If you find yourself stuck on a particular problem, break it down step by step in a notebook. Patience and persistence are key to mastering these subjects. Over time, this practice will significantly enhance your problem-solving abilities.</p> <h3>NCERT Solutions Preparation Tips for All</h3> <p>Subjects like Mathematics are methodical and, at times, philosophical. They involve numerous formulas and steps to arrive at a definitive solution. Thankfully, there are proven techniques to master them!</p> <h3>NCERT Solutions: Your Guide to Competitive Exam Preparation</h3> <p>These tutorials are curated not only to assist students with their board exams but also to prepare for competitive exams like JEE, BITSAT, VITEEE, and more.</p> <p>Students gearing up for competitive exams can leverage these NCERT Solutions to achieve commendable scores. The platform uses image recognition technologies to provide solutions of Maths, Physics, Chemistry, Biology and other subjects. To find the solution to a question, you just have to upload an image of the question. The app uses AI and ML and finds a match it in its database of questions which are pre-answered by in-house experts, and provide you with recorded video solutions.</p><iframe class="w-full h-full id="usage-guildlines"><div class=""><div class="p-2 text-sm marker:dark:text-white"><hr class="mt-0">  <p>Before diving into these NCERT Solutions for Maths, Physics, Chemistry, and Biology, here are some essential tips and tricks to optimize your experience with our video tutorials:</p> <h3> Distraction-Free Study Environment </h3> <p>Subjects like Mathematics, Physics, Chemistry, and Biology demand undivided attention. To make the most of these NCERT video tutorials, ensure you're in a distraction-free study environment. Opt for a serene and noise-free room, which will aid in comprehending and solving intricate problems across all subjects. Moreover, forming a study group with friends can be beneficial. It provides an avenue to discuss and resolve challenging questions together.</p> <h3>Prepare Your Notes</h3> <p>Taking notes while watching the videos is one of the simplest yet most effective strategies. Always have a journal handy to jot down crucial points and formulas. This practice not only aids in information retention but also provides a quick reference for future revisions. Plus, you can always revisit the videos for expert insights!</p> <h3>Face the Doubts</h3> <p>Subjects like Maths are all about practice. If you find yourself stuck on a particular problem, break it down step by step in a notebook. Patience and persistence are key to mastering these subjects. Over time, this practice will significantly enhance your problem-solving abilities.</p> <h3>NCERT Solutions Preparation Tips for All</h3> <p>Subjects like Mathematics are methodical and, at times, philosophical. They involve numerous formulas and steps to arrive at a definitive solution. Thankfully, there are proven techniques to master them!</p> <h3>NCERT Solutions: Your Guide to Competitive Exam Preparation</h3> <p>These tutorials are curated not only to assist students with their board exams but also to prepare for competitive exams like JEE, BITSAT, VITEEE, and more.</p> <p>Students gearing up for competitive exams can leverage these NCERT Solutions to achieve commendable scores. Whenever a concept seems elusive or you're struggling to structure an answer, these videos are your go-to resource. NCERT solutions ka benefit uthayein. Doubtnut aapko deti hai detailed video solutions, jo cover karte hain NCERT Maths, Physics, Chemistry &amp; Biology textbooks ke saare questions har class (Class 6 - Class 12) ke liye. We also cover NCERT Exemplar and NCERT Fingertips book solutions also. Chaahe aap homework kar rahe ho, exams ki taiyari kar rahe ho, ya sirf seekhna chahte ho, hamare detalied solutions Class 10, Class 12 ke PCMB aur usse aage ke liye aapki shiksha yatra ko mazboot&nbsp;banayenge.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="px-4 mt-10 scroll-mt-28" id="complete-syllabus"><h2 class="m-0 mb-4 text-xl sm:text-2xl">Subject wise The platform uses image recognition technologies to provide solutions of Maths, Physics, Chemistry, Biology and other subjects. To find the solution to a question, you just have to upload an image of the question. The app uses AI and ML and finds a match it in its database of questions which are pre-answered by in-house experts, and provide you with recorded video solutions.</p><iframe class="w-full h-full some essential tips and tricks to optimize your experience with our video tutorials:</p> <h3> Distraction-Free Study Environment </h3> <p>Subjects like Mathematics, Physics, Chemistry, and Biology demand undivided attention. To make the most of these NCERT video tutorials, ensure you're in a distraction-free study environment. Opt for a serene and noise-free room, which will aid in comprehending and solving intricate problems across all subjects. Moreover, forming a study group with friends can be beneficial. It provides an avenue to discuss and resolve challenging questions together.</p> <h3>Prepare Your Notes</h3> <p>Taking notes while watching the videos is one of the simplest yet most effective strategies. Always have a journal handy to jot down crucial points and formulas. This practice not only aids in information retention but also provides a quick reference for future revisions. Plus, you can always revisit the videos for expert insights!</p> <h3>Face the Doubts</h3> <p>Subjects like Maths are all about practice. If you find yourself stuck on a particular problem, break it down step by step in a notebook. Patience and persistence are key to mastering these subjects. Over time, this practice will significantly enhance your problem-solving abilities.</p> <h3>NCERT Solutions Preparation Tips for All</h3> <p>Subjects like Mathematics are methodical and, at times, philosophical. They involve numerous formulas and steps to arrive at a definitive solution. Thankfully, there are proven techniques to master them!</p> <h3>NCERT Solutions: Your Guide to Competitive Exam Preparation</h3> <p>These tutorials are curated not only to assist students with their board exams but also to prepare for competitive exams like JEE, BITSAT, VITEEE, and more.</p> <p>Students gearing up for competitive exams can leverage these NCERT Solutions to achieve commendable scores. Distraction-Free Study Environment \u003c/h3\u003e \u003cp\u003eSubjects like Mathematics, Physics, Chemistry, and Biology demand undivided attention. To make the most of these NCERT video tutorials, ensure you're in a distraction-free study environment. Opt for a serene and noise-free room, which will aid in comprehending and solving intricate problems across all subjects. Moreover, forming a study group with friends can be beneficial. It provides an avenue to discuss and resolve challenging questions together.\u003c/p\u003e \u003ch3\u003ePrepare Your Notes\u003c/h3\u003e \u003cp\u003eTaking notes while watching the videos is one of the simplest yet most effective strategies. Always have a journal handy to jot down crucial points and formulas. This practice not only aids in information retention but also provides a quick reference for future revisions. Plus, you can always revisit the videos for expert insights!\u003c/p\u003e \u003ch3\u003eFace the Doubts\u003c/h3\u003e \u003cp\u003eSubjects like Maths are all about practice. If you find yourself stuck on a particular problem, break it down step by step in a notebook. Patience and persistence are key to mastering these subjects. Over time, this practice will significantly enhance your problem-solving abilities.\u003c/p\u003e \u003ch3\u003eNCERT Solutions Preparation Tips for All\u003c/h3\u003e \u003cp\u003eSubjects like Mathematics are methodical and, at times, philosophical. They involve numerous formulas and steps to arrive at a definitive solution. Thankfully, there are proven techniques to master them!\u003c/p\u003e \u003ch3\u003eNCERT Solutions: Your Guide to Competitive Exam Preparation\u003c/h3\u003e \u003cp\u003eThese tutorials are curated not only to assist students with their board exams but also to prepare for competitive exams like JEE, BITSAT, VITEEE, and more.\u003c/p\u003e \u003cp\u003eStudents gearing up for competitive exams can leverage these NCERT Solutions to achieve commendable scores. VITEEE jaise competitive exams ki taiyari ke liye bhi designed hain. Agar aapko koi concept samajh mein nahi aata ya sahi jawab structure nahi kar paate, toh aap in videos ko kabhi bhi, kahin bhi refer kar sakte hain. Adhiktar competitive exams mein sirf NCERT se hi sawal pooche jaate hain. Doubtnut ke experts dwara banaye gaye free Physics, Chemistry, aur Biology video solutions CBSE/NCERT/JEE/IIT guidelines ke anusaar hain. In videos se aap NCERT (Class 6 - Class 12), JEE, IIT jaise exams ke har prashna ka samadhan samajh sakte hain aur apne doubts clear kar sakte hain. Hamare video solutions aapko har subject ke concepts ko aasaan tareeke se samjhaate hain.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="px-4 mt-10  " id="download-app"><div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center items-center gap-1 text-center"><div><div class=""><section class="flex flex-col items-center mt-12"><div class="flex flex-wrap justify-between items-center p-6"><div class="lg:pr-4 lg:basis-2/5"><img alt="Doubtnut on Google Play" src="https://static.doubtnut.com/engagement_framework/22C7A42E-AD8B-D41B-B543-FF93584A9995.webp" width="211" height="65" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="w-full h-auto my-0" loading="lazy" style="color:transparent;background-size:cover;background-position:50% 50%;background-repeat:no-repeat;background-image:url(&quot;data:image/svg+xml;charset=utf-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http%3A//www.w3.org/2000/svg' viewBox='0 0 211 65'%3E%3Cfilter id='b' color-interpolation-filters='sRGB'%3E%3CfeGaussianBlur stdDeviation='20'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Cimage preserveAspectRatio='none' filter='url(%23b)' x='0' y='0' height='100%25' width='100%25' href='data:image/svg+xml;base64,'/%3E%3C/svg%3E&quot;)"></div><div class="lg:px-16 flex flex-col lg:basis-3/5 p-4 items-center"><h3>Download Our App</h3><p>Doubtnut is the No. 1 Study App with India's Best Teachers for Class 6 to 12 upto IIT-JEE, NEET &amp; Other Government Exams. Available on both Android and iOS</p><div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 items-center"><div><a href="https://doubtnut.app.link/X6wgekbjKBb" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener"><img alt="Doubtnut android app on Google Play Store" src="https://play.google.com/intl/en_us/badges/static/images/badges/en_badge_web_generic.png" width="211" height="65" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="w-44 h-auto my-0" loading="lazy" style="color:transparent"></a></div><div><a href="https://tiny.doubtnut.com/iOS-app-3" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener"><img alt="Doubtnut iOS app on App Store" src="https://static.doubtnut.com/engagement_framework/4D6D5BE6-3D00-D2D9-AA03-06E1F488DC39.webp" width="211" height="65" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="w-44 h-auto my-0 px-3" loading="lazy" style="color:transparent"></a></div></div></div></div></section></div></div></div></div><div class="px-4 mt-10" id="about-us"><h2 class="m-0 mb-4 text-xl sm:text-2xl">Who Are We?</h2><div><div><div><p class="">Doubtnut is an Indian educational platform started by Tanushree Nagori and Aditya Shankar in 2016. The platform uses image recognition technologies to provide solutions of Maths, Physics, Chemistry, Biology and other subjects. To find the solution to a question, you just have to upload an image of the question. The app uses AI and ML and finds a match it in its database of questions which are pre-answered by in-house experts, and provide you with recorded video solutions.</p><iframe class="w-full h-full xl:w-[48%] mx-auto aspect-video" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/E_Apuwbny8c" width="500" height="281" title="Who Are We?" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; some essential tips and tricks to optimize your experience with our video tutorials:</p> <h3> Distraction-Free Study Environment </h3> <p>Subjects like Mathematics, Physics, Chemistry, and Biology demand undivided attention. To make the most of these NCERT video tutorials, ensure you're in a distraction-free study environment. Opt for a serene and noise-free room, which will aid in comprehending and solving intricate problems across all subjects. Moreover, forming a study group with friends can be beneficial. It provides an avenue to discuss and resolve challenging questions together.</p> <h3>Prepare Your Notes</h3> <p>Taking notes while watching the videos is one of the simplest yet most effective strategies. Always have a journal handy to jot down crucial points and formulas. This practice not only aids in information retention but also provides a quick reference for future revisions. Plus, you can always revisit the videos for expert insights!</p> <h3>Face the Doubts</h3> <p>Subjects like Maths are all about practice. If you find yourself stuck on a particular problem, break it down step by step in a notebook. Patience and persistence are key to mastering these subjects. Over time, this practice will significantly enhance your problem-solving abilities.</p> <h3>NCERT Solutions Preparation Tips for All</h3> <p>Subjects like Mathematics are methodical and, at times, philosophical. VITEEE jaise competitive exams ki taiyari ke liye bhi designed hain. Agar aapko koi concept samajh mein nahi aata ya sahi jawab structure nahi kar paate, toh aap in videos ko kabhi bhi, kahin bhi refer kar sakte hain. Adhiktar competitive exams mein sirf NCERT se hi sawal pooche jaate hain. Doubtnut ke experts dwara banaye gaye free Physics, Chemistry, aur Biology video solutions CBSE/NCERT/JEE/IIT guidelines ke anusaar hain. In videos se aap NCERT (Class 6 - Class 12), JEE, IIT jaise exams ke har prashna ka samadhan samajh sakte hain aur apne doubts clear kar sakte hain. Hamare video solutions aapko har subject ke concepts ko aasaan tareeke se samjhaate hain.</p></div></div></div></div><div class="px-4 mt-10  " id="download-app"><div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center items-center gap-1 text-center"><div><div class=""><section class="flex flex-col items-center mt-12"><div class="flex flex-wrap justify-between items-center p-6"><div class="lg:pr-4 lg:basis-2/5"><img alt="Doubtnut on Google Play" src="https://static.doubtnut.com/engagement_framework/22C7A42E-AD8B-D41B-B543-FF93584A9995.webp" width="211" height="65" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="w-full h-auto my-0" loading="lazy" style="color:transparent;background-size:cover;background-position:50% 50%;background-repeat:no-repeat;background-image:url(&quot;data:image/svg+xml;charset=utf-8,%3Csvg xmlns='http%3A//www.w3.org/2000/svg' viewBox='0 0 211 65'%3E%3Cfilter id='b' color-interpolation-filters='sRGB'%3E%3CfeGaussianBlur stdDeviation='20'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Cimage preserveAspectRatio='none' filter='url(%23b)' x='0' y='0' height='100%25' width='100%25' href='data:image/svg+xml;base64,'/%3E%3C/svg%3E&quot;)"></div><div class="lg:px-16 flex flex-col lg:basis-3/5 p-4 items-center"><h3>Download Our App</h3><p>Doubtnut is the No. 1 Study App with India's Best Teachers for Class 6 to 12 upto IIT-JEE, NEET &amp; Other Government Exams. Available on both Android and iOS</p><div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 items-center"><div><a href="https://doubtnut.app.link/X6wgekbjKBb" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener"><img alt="Doubtnut android app on Google Play Store" src="https://play.google.com/intl/en_us/badges/static/images/badges/en_badge_web_generic.png" width="211" height="65" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="w-44 h-auto my-0" loading="lazy" style="color:transparent"></a></div><div><a href="https://tiny.doubtnut.com/iOS-app-3" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener"><img alt="Doubtnut iOS app on App Store" src="https://static.doubtnut.com/engagement_framework/4D6D5BE6-3D00-D2D9-AA03-06E1F488DC39.webp" width="211" height="65" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="w-44 h-auto my-0 px-3" loading="lazy" style="color:transparent"></a></div></div></div></div></section></div></div></div></div><div class="px-4 mt-10" id="about-us"><h2 class="m-0 mb-4 text-xl sm:text-2xl">Who Are We?</h2><div><div><div><p class="">Doubtnut is an Indian educational platform started by Tanushree Nagori and Aditya Shankar in 2016. The platform uses image recognition technologies to provide solutions of Maths, Physics, Chemistry, Biology and other subjects. To find the solution to a question, you just have to upload an image of the question. The app uses AI and ML and finds a match it in its database of questions which are pre-answered by in-house experts, and provide you with recorded video solutions.</p><iframe class="w-full h-full xl:w-[48%] mx-auto aspect-video" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/E_Apuwbny8c" width="500" height="281" title="Who Are We?" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; some essential tips and tricks to optimize your experience with our video tutorials:</p> <h3> Distraction-Free Study Environment </h3> <p>Subjects like Mathematics, Physics, Chemistry, and Biology demand undivided attention. To make the most of these NCERT video tutorials, ensure you're in a distraction-free study environment. Opt for a serene and noise-free room, which will aid in comprehending and solving intricate problems across all subjects. Moreover, forming a study group with friends can be beneficial. It provides an avenue to discuss and resolve challenging questions together.</p> <h3>Prepare Your Notes</h3> <p>Taking notes while watching the videos is one of the simplest yet most effective strategies. Always have a journal handy to jot down crucial points and formulas. This practice not only aids in information retention but also provides a quick reference for future revisions. Plus, you can always revisit the videos for expert insights!</p> <h3>Face the Doubts</h3> <p>Subjects like Maths are all about practice. If you find yourself stuck on a particular problem, break it down step by step in a notebook. Patience and persistence are key to mastering these subjects. Over time, this practice will significantly enhance your problem-solving abilities.</p> <h3>NCERT Solutions Preparation Tips for All</h3> <p>Subjects like Mathematics are methodical and, at times, philosophical. They involve numerous formulas and steps to arrive at a definitive solution.
